==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Explicable
<hw>Ex"pli*ca*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>explicabilis</ets>: cf. F. <ets>explicable</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Capable of being explicated; that may be explained or accounted
for; admitting explanation.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> explainable.</syn>
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It is not <qex>explicable</qex> upon any grounds.</q>
<rj><qau>Burke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Explicableness</ent>⟦br⟧
